CLAIM 4: Sum Delta_DS^(4) = 23.796910 +- 1e-6
========================================================================

  True delta values (correct formula, correct ||.||):
    delta_   2 = 0.296570876324497
    delta_   3 = 1.75697196186576
    delta_  19 = 0.530169507106882
    delta_ 191 = 0.169413749026156
  TRUE  sum = 2.7531260943232951007
  PAPER sum = 23.796910
  Difference = 21.043784

  CLAIM 4 VERDICT: WRONG  (true sum ~2.753126, off by 21.044)

  Audit note: The sum 23.796910 would be produced by the wrong formula
  delta_p = -log(||p*pi/10||_WRONG) + log(p)  [two errors: wrong ||.|| + sign]
  For example: paper delta_2 = -log(0.37166359) + log(2) = 0.989644 + 0.693147 = 1.682791
  But definition says: delta_2 = -log(||2*pi/10||) - log(2) = 0.296570876324

