  p_5 = 3.993746e+12  < 6*10^12 = 6.000000e+12
  Paper's claim 'p_5 > 6*10^12' is: WRONG
  True lower bound proven in M4: p_5 > 10^10  (S_4 complete up to 10^10)
  True exact value (certified by M4 prime test): p_5 = 3,993,746,143,633

  The paper's remark 'min(S \ S_4) > 6 * 10^12' overclaims by ~50%.
  Likely origin: rounded from ~4*10^12 to an incorrect '6*10^12'.

